reviewText: a great collection. the most hippest and most happening  tv show ever. there has never been anything like  Soul Train on a  Saturday Morning or afternoon or evening.  this set as the others has  great performances,  great dancing, fashion and it truly captures the time period nicely.

i collect these very happy and bless to have it, the staples singers, freda payne the late marvin gaye with many others artist that i cant think of right now....with fashion, commericals and soultrain dancers......i just enjoy it ......
How wonderful to see the soul train dancers in action, and how great Don Cornelius was.  Glad this is available since his passing.
